        {
            "title": "田北辰睇五月天 讚啟德體育園創造收益無可限量︱Kelly Online",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"田北辰與大女兒和舊同學入場看五月天。田北辰fb\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7c30872a5af4b8210602b1d7c1a59872/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050923015656098.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">田北辰與大女兒和舊同學入場看五月天。田北辰fb</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>台灣天團五月天在啟德主場館開唱，實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰與大女兒和舊同學亦有入場觀看，指音響、燈光都非常正，場內氣氛勁好。他亦透露，今晚一起入場觀看的男拔同學是上周才從三藩市回港，直言啟德主場館讓他大開眼界，一路讚不絕口。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240185/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"田北辰與大女兒和舊同學入場看五月天。田北辰fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1d2c53556912686e455b3edd11b026a/2025-05/495574128_1198410394982624_2330524807137763972_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        田北辰與大女兒和舊同學入場看五月天。田北辰fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240184/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"田北辰與大女兒和舊同學入場看五月天。田北辰fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54c7ad5c3a9ad49b72d1dcd26eadc673/2025-05/495565862_1198410481649282_879738818285078382_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        田北辰與大女兒和舊同學入場看五月天。田北辰fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240186/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"五月天在啟德主場館開唱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ebf0f5108a357357c80aad03395ab80/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250509_181650512.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五月天在啟德主場館開唱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240187/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"田北辰聽聞七成觀眾是內地遊客，且不會即日來回。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/91889c1d02d9be9a990024d7c2b69cb5/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250509_181650512_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        田北辰聽聞七成觀眾是內地遊客，且不會即日來回。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240188/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"田北辰聽聞七成觀眾是內地遊客，且不會即日來回。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3d7e055289c4bbf33eafd16b86711d11/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250509_181650512_07_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        田北辰聽聞七成觀眾是內地遊客，且不會即日來回。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>田北辰在社交平台表示，聽聞不少七成入場觀眾是內地遊客，而且不是即日來回，是專程來港看演唱會，形容全部都是高消費客，認為啟德體育園將來為香港帶來的經濟、旅遊、酒店和餐飲等收益無可限量。\n\n</p>\n<p>他亦指，近年兩岸關係緊張，演藝界交流不免受影響，指出香港在兩岸青年體藝交流的角色變得非常重要，成為「超級聯繫人」。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
